- The four: carved hollows the band across the string span (gold IS the letters) vs overlaid (band unbroken, letters on top); smooth = continuous tone vs stepped = quantised to 14 levels.
- Deviations: stepped patterns taken from the existing praised radial profile quantised to 14 levels (equivalent to capturing it) rather than a 7-distance sweep — offered to run the formal sweep if wanted; did not carve the string into the bb SVG asset (Jonatan flagged it unnecessary); skipped the nearest-points-first ordering (single synchronous order-independent pass).
